    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it still has that fresh, new-car feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for total perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
